# Assets Loans And Receivables Credit Limit Amount

## identifier
de14844

## type
float

## definition
The credit limit is the maximum amount of funds available to the borrower without additional authorisation or approval.

## guidance
This amount should include outstanding balances (including capitalised interest or fees) and any other funds that can be drawn without additional approval by the lender.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.CreditLimit.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.15
- period=instant
